"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president said that the move was requested by Pakistan. He added that the US will keep blocking Iranian ports. This decision was the second time in two weeks that he decided not to escalate the war, giving more time.\",            \"english_title\": \"US and Pakistan Request\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU. dijo que Pakist\u00e1n pidi\u00f3 el movimiento. A\u00f1adi\u00f3 que EE.UU. seguir\u00e1 bloqueando puertos de Ir\u00e1n. Esta decisi\u00f3n fue la segunda vez en dos semanas que decidi\u00f3 no escalar la guerra, dando m\u00e1s tiempo.\",            \"translated_title\": \"EE.UU. y Pakist\u00e1n Piden\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Israel's military announced that two soldiers will be taken off combat duty and will spend 30 days in military detention.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israeli Soldiers Detained\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ej\u00e9rcito de Israel anunci\u00f3 que dos soldados no har\u00e1n servicio de combate y pasar\u00e1n 30 d\u00edas en detenci\u00f3n militar.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Soldados Israel\u00edes Detenidos\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"US envoy Steve Witkoff and Donald Trump's son-in-law Jared Kushner have visited Moscow several times, but they have never been to Kyiv.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Visits to Moscow\",            \"translated_version\": \"El enviado de EE.UU. Steve Witkoff y el yerno de Donald Trump, Jared Kushner, han visitado Mosc\u00fa varias veces, pero nunca han estado en Kyiv.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Visitas de EE.UU. a Mosc\u00fa\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The new maps in Virginia might help Democrats to gain control of the US House of Representatives in November.\",            \"english_title\": \"Virginia Maps and Democrats\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los nuevos mapas en Virginia podr\u00edan ayudar a los dem\u00f3cratas a ganar control de la C\u00e1mara de Representantes de EE.UU. en noviembre.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Mapas de Virginia y Dem\u00f3cratas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The EU's top court ruled that certain reforms violated EU values and broke the founding principles of the EU treaty.\",            \"english_title\": \"EU Court Ruling\",            \"translated_version\": \"El tribunal superior de la UE decidi\u00f3 que ciertas reformas violaron los valores de la UE y rompieron los principios del tratado de la UE.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Decisi\u00f3n del Tribunal de la UE\"        }    ]}"